'''Robin Atkin Downes''' is an [[Wikipedia:British people|British]]-[[Wikipedia:American people|American]] actor and voice actor who played multiple roles in [[Star Wars: The Clone Wars|''The Clone Wars'']] and [[Star Wars Rebels|''Rebels'']].

==Works==
*''[[Star Wars: Bounty Hunter]]'' {{C|Supply ship co-pilot}}
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]'' {{C|[[Griff Vao]], [[Mekel]], additional voices}}
*''[[Star Wars: Rogue Squadron III: Rebel Strike]]'' {{C|[[Sarkli]], Rebel Soldier 1, Stormtrooper 2, Commander 3, Wingman 4}}
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]'' {{C|[[Nikko]], Additional voices}}
*''[[Star Wars: Empire at War: Forces of Corruption]]'' {{C|[[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn]], [[Noghri/Legends|Noghri]]}}
*''[[Rogue One: A Star Wars Story]]'' {{C|Additional Voices}}
*''[[Star Wars Battlefront II]]'' {{C|Additional Voices}}
*''[[Star Wars: Squadrons]]'' {{C|[[Colonel]] [[Gralm]]}}
*{{TBB|Devil's Deal}} {{C|[[Cham Syndulla]]}}
*{{TBB|Rescue on Ryloth (episode)}} {{C|Cham Syndulla}}
*''[[Star Wars Jedi: Survivor]]'' {{C|Additional Voices}}

